data.description: Looking to buy a newer home in a desirable subdivision? You just found it! Located at minutes from all shopping centers on South Preston Hwy: Menards, Lowes, the Cinemark Movie Theater, etc. Beautifully updated with a taste for the fancy. 2 bedrooms with a shared updated bathroom, and a large master bedroom and its also updated master bathroom, plus an additional half bathroom for the guests. Updated kitchen with new cabinets and granite counter tops, modern stainless steel appliances that remain with the home. Gorgeous flooring through-out, updated light fixtures, very convenient kitchenette in the garage, nice rear deck ready for the family cookouts, and more. Don't let this one pass by; it's definitely one to check out, so call your agent now!
